{"tid":2054799,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"我地開左個專講本地新演員嘅channel（2）之今次講佢","createTime":"2020-06-07T12:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:19:52.000Z","uid":122994,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"327bbdcd3877892879853967a4e3d091c583365f","tid":2054799,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"咁多位影視台嘅手足大家好，又係我地Kong Talent Farm團隊，因為上個post已經有一段時間，唔太推得郁，所以索性厚顏無恥地開多個新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道，香港嘅影視圈因為奶共同各種深層次原因，早已經積弱多時，而一個地方嘅軟實力，好大部份都係體現喺該地嘅影視工業度。韓國就係最好嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但相信大家都知道，好似劉華、古老闆、郭富城等老一輩演員嘅極限已經到咗，係一班年輕新演員發揮嘅時候啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我地開左個專門專講本地新演員嘅youtube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望介紹有質素嘅香港新一代俾大家認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地一唔賣慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，二唔情緒勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而係要用實力話畀大家聽一班本地新演員比起老一輩嘅一啲都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而今次介紹嘅演員就係佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kfODG4uj82s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkfODG4uj82s&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=7f0c289c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kfODG4uj82s</a><br />\n<br />\n顧定軒，年紀輕輕已經出演過唔少院線電影，而且演出嘅好多都係衝獎級別嘅高難度角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然佢嘅表演甚至比一啲資深演員更好，但似乎都唔係畀一般觀眾認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以我哋特登整咗呢條片，希望等更多嘅人認識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家睇片之餘，亦都多多廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e192d8ce2b9182ac1424e98b7e7849fec83b5dd","tid":2054799,"uid":122994,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BgdiW87S5T4&amp;t=9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBgdiW87S5T4%26t%3D9s&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=1745032a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BgdiW87S5T4&amp;t=9s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我哋上一段片，講嘅係啱啱播完嘅《寂寞是幫兇》嘅主角，Alma郭爾君，未睇嘅都希望多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，都要利申一下，我哋團隊成員都係純義工，呢班演員如果有錢做PR IG就唔會得萬零follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea02dc4d1e6f9a143476d5b4aaad17f70edd1ab6","tid":2054799,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"另外我地開左個fb group歡迎大家入黎閒時吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/groups/323072035375960?tsid=0.23786080785891883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fgroups%2F323072035375960%3Ftsid%3D0.23786080785891883&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=cc39e31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/groups/323072035375960?tsid=0.23786080785891883</a>"},{"pid":"d18f065a1e94b734e3f6ea85fef707cae314a875","tid":2054799,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"咁舊嗰個仲推唔推?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b054b621433b82ee52a34992fb7ea6f0edb5dfde","tid":2054799,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d18f065a1e94b734e3f6ea85fef707cae314a875","tid":2054799,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"咁舊嗰個仲推唔推?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep